data.description: Welcome to your dream colonial-style home! This stunning property is situated on a generous corner lot, boasting mature trees that provide shade and serenity. The roof has been recently replaced as well! The exterior is complemented by a delightful garden and cozy firepit area, perfect for enjoying outdoor gatherings with friend and family. Additionally, a spacious bac deck with a charming pergola awaits, offering an ideal spot for relaxation and entertaining. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The main floor features a family room, an open kitchen & dining space that provide a seamless flow, making it effortless to entertain guests while preparing delicious meals. Convenience is at its best with a main floor half bath. Venturing to the second floor, you'll find 4 bedrooms and a full bathroom to cater to the needs of the entire household. The basement is unfinished, presenting a world of possibilities to suit your specific needs. To complete the package, the home includes an attached two-car garage.
